    <p class="lead">The best AeroPress brew time for most people is shorter than they think. You do not need to let it sit forever. In fact, once you get past the sweet spot, the cup can go from bright and juicy to flat and woody fast. For a balanced everyday brew, start around 75 to 90 seconds total contact time, then tweak from there based on what lands in your mug.</p>
